The Postmaster of Mafdet has received an open commission for a complete route survey of the Arroyo. The dry riverbed approaches and the terrain within the Arroyo are imperfectly documented in the harbor authority's reference files, and expeditions operating in the area have reported routing difficulties. Survey every accessible section and return with a complete navigation record.
Your Arroyo survey has been filed with Mafdet's harbor authority reference office. The route record has been incorporated into the expedition documentation used by crews departing Mafdet for the eastern approaches, and the postmaster has closed the open commission.
